OL,3,CUefa charge Derry City and CSKA Sofia
OL,4,Cover Europa League match violence
OL,6,FDerry City have been warned they could
OL,7,Fface supporter bans after violence
OL,8,Fmarred their Europa League match with
OL,9,FCSKA Sofia.
OL,11,FGoverning body Uefa charged both clubs
OL,12,Fover the trouble which saw a pitch
OL,13,Finvasion, missiles thrown and attempts
OL,14,Fby away fans to storm the home stand.
OL,15,FFans of the Bulgarian team have also
OL,16,Fbeen accused of racist or
OL,17,Fdiscriminatory behaviour.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
