OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784321282
OL,3,CUefa charge Derry City and CSKA Sofia
OL,4,Cover Europa League match violence
OL,6,FPSNI riot officers were deployed to
OL,7,Fthe stadium after trouble flared in
OL,8,Fthe Bishop Street area an hour before
OL,9,Fthe qualifier match kicked off.
OL,11,FThe match, which CSKA Sofia won 2-1 to
OL,12,Fseal a 5-3 aggregate victory, then had
OL,13,Fto be paused for 14 minutes during the
OL,14,Fsecond half as further trouble broke
OL,15,Fout in the stands.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
