FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784321282
OL,3,CUefa charge Derry City and CSKA Sofia
OL,4,Cover Europa League match violence
OL,6,FPSNI chief inspector Graeme Craig
OL,7,Fsaid: "Disorder initially broke out
OL,8,Fbetween rival football supporters in
OL,9,Fthe Bishop Street area prior to kick-
OL,10,Foff at around 6.45pm and,
OL,11,Funfortunately, one of our officers was
OL,12,Finjured and required hospital
OL,13,Ftreatment.
OL,15,F"During the second half of the fixture
OL,16,Ffurther disorder occurred between
OL,17,Frival fans within the stadium, causing
OL,18,Fthe match to be paused for
OL,19,Fapproximately 14 minutes.
OL,26,@oD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784321282
OL,3,CUefa charge Derry City and CSKA Sofia
OL,4,Cover Europa League match violence
OL,6,F"At the request of Derry City Football
OL,7,FClub, and in the interests of public
OL,8,Fsafety, police officers were deployed
OL,9,Finside the stadium to manage the
OL,10,Fsituation and restore calm, meaning
OL,11,Fthat the match could continue to its
OL,12,Fconclusion."
OL,14,FChief inspector Craig added: "It is
OL,15,Fdisappointing that an important and
OL,16,Fhigh-profile European sporting fixture
OL,17,Fshould be disrupted in such a manner.
OL,19,F"I'm sure all right-thinking football
OL,20,Fsupporters will join me in condemning
OL,21,Fsuch behaviour.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@LO]vD@^OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
