PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784321282
OL,3,CUefa charge Derry City and CSKA Sofia
OL,4,Cover Europa League match violence
OL,6,F"Sport is such an integral part of our
OL,7,Fcommunity and we have seen a vibrant
OL,8,Fand excited mood in the city
OL,9,Fthroughout the day. Regrettably, this
OL,10,Fevening we` have witnessed families
OL,11,Fand young children seeking refuge on
OL,12,Fthe pitch because of the unacceptable
OL,13,Fand reckless behaviour of a small
OL,14,Fnumber of individuals.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
