FL,414,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784321282
OL,3,CUefa charge Derry City and CSKA Sofia
OL,4,Cover Europa League match violence
OL,6,F"We would advise members of the public
OL,7,Fthat there will be a continued police
OL,8,Fpresence in the area tonight."Police
OL,9,Fasked for witnesses to contact them by
OL,10,Fcalling 101 or by contacting
OL,11,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555
OL,12,F111.
OL,14,FDerry City Football Club have said
OL,15,Fthey "unequivocally condemn the
OL,16,Fviolence".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
