OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1784321282
OL,3,CUefa charge Derry City and CSKA Sofia
OL,4,Cover Europa League match violence
OL,6,FA statement read: "The club is working
OL,7,Fclosely with UEFA, the PSNI, CSKA
OL,8,FSofia and our security partners to
OL,9,Festablish the full facts surrounding
OL,10,Fthe incidents.
OL,12,F"In the interests of ensuring a
OL,13,Fthorough investigation, Derry City
OL,14,FFootball Club will make no further
OL,15,Fcomment until this process has been
OL,16,Fconcluded."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
