OL,3,CUefa charge Derry City and CSKA Sofia
OL,4,Cover Europa League match violence
OL,6,FA UEFA statement read: "As the
OL,7,Fproceedings could have an impact on
OL,8,Fsupporter attendance at future
OL,9,Fmatches, the UEFA Disciplinary bodies
OL,10,Fwill decide on the matter early next
OL,11,Fweek."
